## #msi-cells

**Value type:** `<u32>`

The *#msi-cells* property defines the number of cells required to encode an MSI specifier for this MSI controller. Used by MSI controller nodes to indicate how many `<u32>` cells follow the phandle in `msi-parent` references.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
pcie0_msi: msi-controller@1c0e0040 {
    compatible = "qcom,pcie-msi";
    #msi-cells = <1>;
};
```
